{
  "stem": "2735.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I also remember that Pole-- the Poles and then I was older already-- that the Poles came out, that they shoot, concentrate to get a business in Polish hands.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and that Poles should buy from Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, this is-- so across the street from us, they opened a business, the same as ours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And put in, like, a cut out of a human-sized person that it said was the slogan, 'buy only from a Polack.' And I guess this really made us to-- made my parents to start to think about moving away somewhere else because--",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'36, '35, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I could be younger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't last more than a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- but that was-- then the Ukranian in our town were very nationalistic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, we heard Ukranian talk in a language that was-- that the Poles probably would listen to it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to leave on consignment, paintings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very good paintings, the Ukranian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They usual-- they used to leave a lot of-- but they had those national-- national teams of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "About their heroes like Shevchenko.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the Ukranians, we were scared more than the Poles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the Poles considered themselves sort of aristocracy, blue blood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, the Ukrainians, everybody knew were the peasants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that probably was my impression, but that probably wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They probably had between-- because you can see today, they have a country and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in my mind, they were the peasants.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, we left the city, and we went to big-- live in a big down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have relatives there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father completely had a new way of making a living.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was doing business with Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the center of textile.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
